    <div style="font-size:12px; color:#2563eb; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin-bottom:12px;">— Tools —</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:32px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;">框架与工具</h1>
    <p style="color:#64748b; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:36px; max-width:600px;">主流 Agent 框架的深度对比、选型决策指南与最佳实践。</p>
    <div style="background:white; border:1.5px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:40px; text-align:center; color:#94a3b8; font-size:14px;">
      工具版块构建中。<br>将涵盖 LangGraph、CrewAI、Dify、AutoGen、MCP 等。
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
